The '''Natori Shock Troops''' were a [[Mercenary/Legends|mercenary]] unit allied with the [[Natori Association]]. Graduates of the Natori Association's training programs usually paid for the cost of their training by serving a tour with the Natori Shock Troops, while entrants who paid for the training up front went on to serve in other units.<ref name="J15">{{JournalCite|15|Special Military Unit Intelligence Update}}</ref>

